<paragraph blockId="9.[151,1436,1687,1999]" pageId="9" pageNumber="65">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,312,1904,1928]" inLineHeading="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="65" reason="1">Remarks.</emphasis>
This species was described based on 
<specimenCount box="[744,909,1903,1927]" pageId="9" pageNumber="65" type="generic">two specimens</specimenCount>
from the same locality, 
<collectingCountry box="[1187,1240,1904,1927]" name="Peru" pageId="9" pageNumber="65">Peru</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingRegion box="[1253,1326,1903,1927]" country="Peru" name="Cusco" pageId="9" pageNumber="65">Cuzco</collectingRegion>
. Both are deposited in Dresden. One of them is designated 
<typeStatus box="[685,788,1939,1963]" pageId="9" pageNumber="65">lectotype</typeStatus>
accordingly to fix and stabilize the current concept of the name.
</paragraph>
